    Surplus production

    sp.Rd

    Calculates the surplus production.

    # S4 method for FLBRP,missing,ANY
sp(stock, rel = TRUE)

    Arguments

    m

    An object of class FLBRP

    Value

    object of class FLQuant with sp estimate

    See also

    FLCore::sp()
